Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把小光还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别为难我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是新星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将要杀死小光的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第30话 新星与恶魔魔神雷卡利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午安 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是新星 将要杀死你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想见你 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为过去都只能在梦中跟你讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈终于准许我跟你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是迪波尼亚妈妈呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们一定要相互厮杀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我最喜欢你了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是欧多札姆来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说 从法连？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇杰达？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在锡菲罗的旁边诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来杀死小光的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱 小光惨叫的声音 我太喜欢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再叫出更可爱的声音给我听呀 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一样的魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以使用跟你一样的所有魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是小光嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟小光一样哦 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拜托妈妈 做了好东西给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷卡利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔神？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼唤我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的力量已超出你想像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼唤我的名字吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个真的是魔神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是魔神？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:08:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不够！再多跟我玩一会儿！小光！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护之风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢妨碍我跟小光玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是小光喜欢的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在小光面前杀死你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异空间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异空间？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这里是锡菲罗却又不是锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是你们魔神所待的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是我们所在的异空间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新星创造出来的空间？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新星？那个女生叫做新星？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在谈什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准其他女孩和她要好！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么小光是你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光是我的 只可以跟我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀死她们俩人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢伤害小海跟小风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 我…我是喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想跟你玩而已呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想杀死你而已呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是别的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心 邪恶之气又高涨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么小心呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要逃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏我想杀死你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人杀还感到高兴的人 才是有毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们迟早会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不一定是我们死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚疾风！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是「她」创造出来的异空间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的魔法力量会减半
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温达姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光你会了解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤害小海跟小风…我最重要的同伴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是绝不饶恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗就快成为我妈妈的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈的？这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪波尼亚妈妈等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待锡菲罗的支柱消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家的所有人陷入不安恐惧 输给自己内心的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输给自己内心？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光必须跟我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼中只准有我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大的邪恶力量来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦中出现的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我是在你梦中出现的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 她怎么知道我心中的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洞察人心不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异世界的少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想拯救锡菲罗的 传说中的魔法骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的存在是锡菲罗的人们 所期盼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩溃的时间接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家再过几个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当砂漏的砂子漏光时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都会消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要的是彻底的毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无尽的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高贵的虚无空间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士的传说只会妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可爱的女儿 新星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想看看魔法骑士的红色鲜血呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光的血！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱的新星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把锡菲罗的支柱都打不倒的魔法骑士传说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉碎掉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在你们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你们身边等着你们死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部死光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 我最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是小光喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全部都讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你别太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说要让你杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会被你的笑容所骗的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说 你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要跟我们为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惩戒之风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才妈妈说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们住在锡菲罗的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在锡菲罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没注意到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就这么的靠近呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士的剑 这么简单就断掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再练强一点吧 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时再来陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后会有期了 魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次碰面时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定杀死你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个邪恶的气是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笼罩锡菲罗整体的邪恶之气究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在锡菲罗的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 锡菲罗本身也有那个气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位小姐消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光是可爱的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来能成为魔法骑士的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只有 召唤自异世界的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有支柱 就不能成立的锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为是不正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想把你当敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该作了魔法防御了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不中他的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札兹 你喜欢的小姐走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好不容易 帮小光做了一套新衣服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 被兰迪斯的那双眼睛一看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很心虚 我的决心差点就动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管有什么借口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侵略他国 并不是一件可以开心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的甜食全部送你 打起精神来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连藏在房间的也要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:24.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如吹越广大海洋的风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:32.84,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的梦放出数不清的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:35.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不管任何时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:39.02,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,执意隐藏起受伤的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:43.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,迎向明天的白色背影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:47.35,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,令我再也看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:51.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,让我轻轻地抹掉你的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:54.86,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,让我轻轻地拥抱你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:23:02.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的胸中获得安憩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.37,0:23:06.04,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll give you I'll give you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.04,0:23:17.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,歇起翅膀 梦还是不会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:20.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll give you I'll give you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:25.29,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有相信的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:29.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能够帮助你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:38.91,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll give you my love Lullaby
